    "page_or_timestamp": "181-210",
    "content": "Kelly Criterion: f* = (p - (1-p)/R) / 1 = (p*R - (1-p)) / R\n\nExplanation: Where p=win probability, R=win/loss ratio. If p=0.6, R=1.5, f*=(0.6*1.5-0.4)/1.5=0.37 (37% of capital)",
    "content_type": "formula",
